modDescription:
This mod only does one thing!

It increases scraping speed by 10x, this applies to iron/brass/lead/clay/glass/wood.

Since it was created as a patch, it should work with almost any other mod and should work for future 7d2d releases, unless they change something major.

Since it contains only xml files, itâ€™s EAC safe and server-side. no need for client to download it.
